   "type": "text",
   "x": 40,
   "y": 520,
   "width": 1647.03,
   "height": 15,
   "text": "Prometheus scrapes each node exporter on TCP 9100 plus the Proxmox API exporter every 15 seconds. The repository assertion script requires exactly these seven jobs, requires every one UP, and rejects the retired addresses so a stale target can't slip back in.",
